SECRET_KEY=your-very-long-secret-key-minimum-50-chars
DEBUG=False
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname
REDIS_URL=redis://default:password@host:port
ALLOWED_HOSTS=yourdomain.onrender.com,www.yourdomain.com
```

---

## Where to set env variables on Render (the actual answer)

You do **not** upload `.env.production` to Render. Instead:

**Dashboard → Your Service → Environment tab → Add Environment Variable**
```
SECRET_KEY        →  paste a 50+ char random key
DEBUG             →  False
DATABASE_URL      →  auto-filled if you use Render's PostgreSQL add-on
REDIS_URL         →  auto-filled if you use Render's Redis add-on
ALLOWED_HOSTS     →  pixel-social.onrender.com